# Offline Authentication Patch for Prism
#
# This patch enables offline mode by:
# 1. Bypassing Mojang session validation
# 2. Generating offline UUIDs from username
# 3. Using --accessToken 0 as launch argument
#
# The game is launched with these arguments:
#   --username <name> --accessToken 0 --version Prism
#
# This makes the client skip online authentication
# and use a locally-generated UUID for the player profile.
